Sa Hildebrandslied was meliths in thizoei aldái thiudiskarazdái in thamma antharamma daila thizos ahtaudins jerahunda. Sa ist spill bi sarwadrauhts Hildebrand. Is bigitith sunus is, Hadubrand, ana andsokastada, akei ni saíhvand sik jah andweihand. 

